{"id": 1775, "genre": 1000, "title": "你最近发现当代明星又有哪些新型热门人设？", "description": "最近的明星宣传文案，又有哪些新写法？请在评论区补充。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 13116, "comment_count": 80, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170702182012SqlwmKacuiyxk2BN.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-02T17:00:43Z", "questions": [{"id": 2534, "title": "你最近发现当代明星又有哪些新型热门人设？", "content": "当代明星又有哪些新型热门人设？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 217642, "content": "高情商，幽默机智会说话", "image": "img/option/option/20170630151525M2vAw9c8biKlPm4k.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 217643, "content": "气质型，不以美貌取胜，与妖艳贱货不同", "image": "img/option/option/201706301533278iOh1KIBjTcJoQEg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 217645, "content": "忧郁且不羁，现实世界不得志，多见于民谣歌手", "image": "img/option/option/20170630153720mWV5ic8QNMAFf39Y.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 217646, "content": "正能量，健康向上，“努力”，肤白，为年轻人树立榜样", "image": "img/option/option/201706301540306qI4BdhXuJ57YLpV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 217647, "content": "老顽童，人老心不老，和年轻人打成一片", "image": "img/option/option/20170630154159klzXumUyGvDa5jrV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 217654, "content": "淡薄名利不争高低，守住内心净土", "image": "img/option/option/20170630154351dTftsrKVP0yeOYW4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 217655, "content": "耿直boy / girl，为人率真大大咧咧", "image": "img/option/option/20170630154926M6p8cK9zXZjSieVY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 217656, "content": "少年感，年岁渐长却依然保持纯真青涩", "image": "img/option/option/20170630155336I1WeH2UwzsiVS7Yr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}